{"type": "article", "id": 21125, "title": "芒果沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-22T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 52, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060615395025WBLS0jkTNarIu3.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这张沙发是丹麦一家新成立的设计品牌 WON 为瑞典的设计工作室 Note Design studio 设计的。Mango 是芒果，它的椭圆造型和十字纹路的确有剥开芒果之后的感觉，很贴切。相较于古典式的沙发，它多了一份清新自然和活泼的气氛，也能捕捉到年轻的人群。它有深蓝色和浅棕色两种颜色。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153948gMeXY2owBQUzi3uG.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69095477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153949pR8WGn9uPHBYtidT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.69095477\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153949K7GSx1bmXJQTUnkR.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.36829268\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606153950rf6QdIcpL14s8Mxe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.36956522\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}